Programs running behind the scenes are called Daemons

To debug failure cause, command that can be used is: journalctl -xe


 Security Enhanced Linux - developed by NSA
 Biggest security in the terms of service level file level security

 SE Linux hold port no. associated with diff servers in its DB.
 Webserver must use 80


getenforce - to get the status of SE Linux
setenforce - 1/0 - to enable or disable the SE Linux

nmap used to scap IPs and Port no.s to identify active ports
